@startuml
!theme plain

actor "顧客" as Customer
participant "システム" as System
database "カート" as Cart
database "注文" as Order
database "注文明細" as OrderLine
boundary "注文完了画面" as OrderCompleteScreen

== 注文を確定する ==
Customer -> System : 注文を確定する
activate System
group transaction (inferred from FK)
System -> Order : create
System -> OrderLine : create
end
System -> Cart : update
note right : FK非連結 — 別TX？API境界で明示を
System --> Customer : 注文完了画面
deactivate System

@enduml
